{
  "id": "RAW_f164a9",
  "title": "GPT-5 的路由器：工作原理以及前沿实验室如何利用帕累托前沿",
  "url": "https://www.latent.space/p/gpt5-router",
  "date": "2025-08-07 20:23:38",
  "author": "Latent.Space",
  "siteName": "Latent Space",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p><span>We have been the most vocal </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/reasoning-price-war?utm_source=publication-search\" rel=\"\">proponents of the intelligence pareto frontier</a><span> since the start of the reasoning model era. </span><a href=\"https://x.com/demishassabis/status/1908301867672560087\" rel=\"\">Demis took note</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://x.com/demishassabis/status/1913013113630110093\" rel=\"\">GDM went for it</a><span>.</span><strong> But with GPT-5, OpenAI now dominates the intelligence per dollar frontier for the first time.</strong></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!toeh!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe585c017-9a82-4a05-b339-d0e76d507a2b_1672x1236.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fe6aae25-dc5e-407d-82d7-ee36b36e2800/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ed6feb72-e4cb-4501-11a9-5faa670d4600/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3a5e4a9d-c8c2-4c13-6d1d-41b039948f00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/657709c1-399c-4001-b842-9b293c216900/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7dd2900-ca35-4b53-d824-43c4de33c300/public\" width=\"727.9948120117188\" height=\"537.9961660196493\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e585c017-9a82-4a05-b339-d0e76d507a2b_1672x1236.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;normal&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:1076,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:727.9948120117188,&quot;bytes&quot;:338105,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/170387696?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe585c017-9a82-4a05-b339-d0e76d507a2b_1672x1236.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;center&quot;,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ee244f9c-0e92-4f0b-1d1b-1c6397528000/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/201f5cb3-b831-4875-937a-21c2e22e6f00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/878fda0f-0abc-4487-a363-d63887ee8200/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7dd2900-ca35-4b53-d824-43c4de33c300/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n     <figcaption class=\"image-caption\">\n      <span>Gemini </span><a href=\"https://news.smol.ai/issues/25-05-20-google-io\" rel=\"\">lasted all of 3 months</a><span> at the pareto frontier</span>\n     </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>When we first tried it out, </span><a href=\"https://x.com/OpenAIDevs/status/1953535155789865423\" rel=\"\">those of us in the developer beta</a><span> were initially concerned - “it’s a great coding model… but is that it?” was kind of the unspoken elephant in the room. Sentiment turned more positive over time and the big aha that got me fully hyped was the pricing reveal. </span></p>\n   <p><strong>This is because the $ per intelligence frontier is ultimately a routing problem; </strong><span>one that has been a developing and increasingly optimized story since the introduction of GPT-4 and o1.</span></p>\n   <p><span>The #1 question that people have about GPT-5 being “unified” is “</span><strong>is it a router??</strong><span>”, a question I have asked both </span><a href=\"https://youtu.be/avWhreBUYF0\" rel=\"\">Greg Brockman</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/noam-brown\" rel=\"\">Noam Brown</a><span>, and after a lot of back and forth on Twitter and inconclusive answers, we now have the answer right there in </span><a href=\"https://openai.com/index/gpt-5-system-card/\" rel=\"\">the GPT-5 system card</a><span>: </span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!4g2w!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4238c3fa-4e3f-4823-9b92-d0cc7025b4df_969x807.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c9174901-cd27-4f0a-3475-8aa8df334900/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/31a3cae0-d3bd-4ed1-5627-79f046a70200/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1f5856e5-445e-4687-7888-4cff045f1600/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/89c296b7-b1b1-45c9-15e5-ef9884f47700/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/04e64f95-04fc-4c8f-dab6-1695cb4dc300/public\" width=\"969\" height=\"807\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4238c3fa-4e3f-4823-9b92-d0cc7025b4df_969x807.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:807,&quot;width&quot;:969,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:115876,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/170387696?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4238c3fa-4e3f-4823-9b92-d0cc7025b4df_969x807.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/59ac7186-f575-45d2-eab4-9377d870f600/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ef3cff9f-c514-42cb-4f14-60600a4da800/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ad7b21f9-d248-4c0d-b850-fa6211544300/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/04e64f95-04fc-4c8f-dab6-1695cb4dc300/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>This is a level of transparency I had been asking for from the team, but was never really optimistic about getting!</p>\n   <p><strong>To really drive it home:</strong></p>\n   <p><span>If the big breakthrough from GPT-3 to </span><a href=\"https://x.com/swyx/status/1671272883379908608\" rel=\"\">GPT-4 was the Mixture of Experts</a><span>, then perhaps </span><strong>the big breakthrough from GPT-4o/o3 to GPT-5 is the Mixture of Models (aka the “router”).</strong></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!dsKb!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3c57d4b-ba61-4ad4-bd8a-2b5dfcb54161_2676x1372.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7bad43ba-8b76-4c95-ba23-fdb7cd439900/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/989bb7a2-80af-4541-e4c1-aa50d8dbd900/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/eedeec93-0a0d-407a-6562-9d4a80e90c00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f8dc513e-fd11-4397-f8d0-bbf5eef34a00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/79e7bf78-a5bb-48f1-a76d-7e6e16137c00/public\" width=\"1200\" height=\"614.8351648351648\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3c57d4b-ba61-4ad4-bd8a-2b5dfcb54161_2676x1372.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:false,&quot;imageSize&quot;:&quot;large&quot;,&quot;height&quot;:746,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:1200,&quot;bytes&quot;:356924,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/170387696?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3c57d4b-ba61-4ad4-bd8a-2b5dfcb54161_2676x1372.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;center&quot;,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5f3862a2-f8d3-427a-7214-bd2422c04500/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/01e55fe2-b69c-4fed-8578-b7bf670de000/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12d47d70-1965-4af6-5bcc-3fae11c53000/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7e01efc3-2169-48b6-8e7a-c7e23c060800/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-large\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Why does it matter? \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/170387696/why-does-it-matter\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>To some extent, whether or not GPT5 is a “unified model” or “unified system”, whether or not there’s a component that you call a “router” point blank, doesn’t quite matter. The moment you have reasoning and non reasoning modes, the moment you have different paths for inference for efficiency or specialization (“experts”) or </span><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2404.02258\" rel=\"\">compute depth</a><a data-component-name=\"FootnoteAnchorToDOM\" id=\"footnote-anchor-1-170387696\" href=\"https://www.latent.space/p/gpt5-router#footnote-1-170387696\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"\" class=\"footnote-anchor\">1</a><span>, you essentially have a router somewhere in the system, and now it is just a question of semantics and “thickness” of the router layer.</span></p>\n   <p>For example you can see the MoE layer in open source models like Qwen 3, where it is clearly routing.</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!8spu!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3dcf98b9-5d19-4531-befe-1cfc8ffffd6e_5906x4341.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/593f424f-d3e5-4b35-47da-1c7028ddea00/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8464d50c-62fe-4058-8aaa-579e2e75bc00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cbd68459-5a42-4c5a-635b-221fbcba3800/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6977488a-85e8-4c50-8d00-6a9558d9bb00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ad9fcf5d-c564-44a8-35c8-51a054d40400/public\" width=\"362\" height=\"266.0302197802198\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3dcf98b9-5d19-4531-befe-1cfc8ffffd6e_5906x4341.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1070,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:362,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/56573773-89db-48e0-e9c4-53debbf7e600/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17bc525b-d6f9-4ff0-8588-55e6fb1ed100/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e8eebd09-7e03-4703-f8dd-be1096ccce00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ad9fcf5d-c564-44a8-35c8-51a054d40400/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n     <figcaption class=\"image-caption\">\n      <span>from </span><a href=\"https://substack.com/@rasbt\" rel=\"\">@rasbt’s excellent substack</a>\n     </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>So even though there’s DEFINITELY a router, one benefit and reason why people are still extremely curious about it is the ability to lock down parts of the model performance and independently progress them.</p>\n   <p>So for example, if GPT5 = router + “new 4o” + “new o3”, then (if we had control of the weights) if a bug happened there are only 3 sources of error:</p>\n   <ol>\n    <li>\n     <p>did it route to the right model?</p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p>if it was a nonreasoner bug, can we fix that?</p></li>\n    <li>\n     <p>if it was a reasoner bug, can we fix that?</p></li>\n   </ol>\n   <p>And because these are “orthogonal” independently moving pieces, you can expect that improving one while holding the other constant is an intuitive important step to engineering better AI systems.</p>\n   <p><span>Perhaps most comforting (or disappointing?) to the rest of us </span><a href=\"https://x.com/deedydas/status/1953318528385167695\" rel=\"\">non-OpenAI-millionaires</a><span> is that </span><em>that’s how we would do this too</em><span>, and there is no big secret that the BigLabs have been hiding that there is a more Bitter Lesson-y way to make hybrid models.</span></p>\n   <p></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!oIbA!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1643dfbc-8a6a-4306-bcca-be41448229aa_391x103.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f367ab63-c44d-448b-f9c0-3c680a71ab00/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e2d39a6a-d155-4ca6-5beb-5e7c5220f100/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1dc4706e-b4b3-4208-10e0-5369a1911e00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a516ff21-7e40-460b-cc25-37a9c742fc00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/764c889c-ef8a-4be6-b778-986ed5d4ad00/public\" width=\"391\" height=\"103\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1643dfbc-8a6a-4306-bcca-be41448229aa_391x103.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:103,&quot;width&quot;:391,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:16779,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/170387696?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1643dfbc-8a6a-4306-bcca-be41448229aa_391x103.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb0b44cf-42e8-4c42-fcdc-eadd6c367900/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c50b4fbe-1e61-42b6-eeb6-fb147e763200/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/45c79656-1ee5-4200-44fb-0f859625e300/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/764c889c-ef8a-4be6-b778-986ed5d4ad00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n      </div></a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">The Great Consolidation \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://www.latent.space/i/170387696/the-great-consolidation\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg></button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p><span>The immediate benefit of the GPT-5 launch is a question of cognitive load - as you can tell </span><a href=\"https://x.com/swyx/status/1922797421484011758\" rel=\"\">the model picker mess</a><span> weighs heavily on OpenAI and a unified system starts to fix it (even though for developers, control remains as the “model picker” effectively shifts into </span><a href=\"https://cookbook.openai.com/examples/gpt-5/gpt-5_new_params_and_tools\" rel=\"\">the new reasoning effort, verbosity, function calling params</a><span>):</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!EliP!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72a6594c-d3f8-4f56-9368-38154bde9601_2428x1252.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/297180bf-480f-4cf8-b0f0-1280cccdd200/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7a4adfd5-96a9-4189-9148-b699b35cfc00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1afe6e0e-452d-49fa-47c0-cb78b3fd1500/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/74b61337-e31d-4ed9-4060-3009f5cb5f00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7053fd74-fa1a-4b99-d07d-898a29b15f00/public\" width=\"1456\" height=\"751\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/72a6594c-d3f8-4f56-9368-38154bde9601_2428x1252.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:751,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:334853,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/170387696?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72a6594c-d3f8-4f56-9368-38154bde9601_2428x1252.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/678c1d0d-603a-4996-3207-aaef49660900/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a8c0bbc9-1293-453f-3d70-5b732c3cea00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/236ac078-c2bb-4b20-5a9d-921bcb7f5400/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7053fd74-fa1a-4b99-d07d-898a29b15f00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <p><span>This is backed up by </span><a href=\"https://help.openai.com/en/articles/6825453-chatgpt-release-notes\" rel=\"\">impending model deprecations</a><span> confirmed in release notes:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!kpC9!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdea0adc0-faf8-45ed-96db-8c51545aa11e_1824x1016.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\">\n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture>\n        <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4c5d9bbb-447e-4c65-2be2-8965e63d4900/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/23753248-ed2b-402f-b357-0fab1dbb5100/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0db001c4-ca3d-4434-7b2a-ea1ca2bafc00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95d54c4a-e578-4433-cd14-3841144c9700/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\">\n        <img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/67f85cb2-74e0-4ace-d9aa-1acc53688000/public\" width=\"1456\" height=\"811\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/dea0adc0-faf8-45ed-96db-8c51545aa11e_1824x1016.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:811,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:131005,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://www.latent.space/i/170387696?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdea0adc0-faf8-45ed-96db-8c51545aa11e_1824x1016.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a12ec102-1c0d-4d60-ab7a-ed896fe95700/public 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f2a71c4c-d6c8-4465-1a3b-9785d3e59100/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/315f4e7b-05ff-4d28-fc72-acb4e7166800/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/67f85cb2-74e0-4ace-d9aa-1acc53688000/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\">\n       </picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div></a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p></p>\n   <p>Which is a -far- more ambitious deprecation schedule than the Developer facing options, with all their permutations:</p>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章揭示了 GPT-5 的核心创新在于“混合模型”（路由器），它优化了单位成本智能，简化了模型使用，并促进了模块化人工智能系统的开发。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章揭示了 GPT-5 的核心创新在于“混合模型”（路由器），它优化了单位成本智能，简化了模型使用，并促进了模块化人工智能系统的开发。",
  "summary": "本文认为，GPT-5 的重大进步在于其“混合模型”架构，实际上是一个“路由器”，这使得 OpenAI 在单位成本智能方面处于领先地位。文章认为，实现具有成本效益的智能本质上是一个路由问题。这个路由器概念，是从混合专家 (MoE) 演变而来，允许 GPT-5 动态地将查询定向到专门的子模型（例如，推理模型与非推理模型）。作者强调了关键优势：能够独立开发和调试不同的模型组件，并通过模型的“统一化”简化用户体验。虽然开发人员通过新的参数保留了精细的控制，但最终用户在模型选择方面面临的认知负担较小。文章表明，这种混合方法并非秘密，而是领先的人工智能实验室中的一种常见策略。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "GPT-5 的“混合模型”（路由器）架构优化了单位成本智能的领先地位。",
      "explanation": "这种创新的路由机制允许 OpenAI 通过动态地利用针对不同任务的专门子模型，以具有竞争力的成本有效地提供高智能，从而树立了新的行业基准。"
    },
    {
      "point": "路由器架构有助于人工智能模型组件的独立开发、调试和改进。这简化了开发流程。",
      "explanation": "通过将请求路由到不同的、专门的模型，开发人员可以隔离和增强特定功能或修复错误，而不会影响整个统一系统，从而简化了工程流程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GPT-5 的统一系统通过各种模型的“统一化”简化了用户体验。",
      "explanation": "尽管内部复杂，但基于路由器的架构降低了最终用户在模型选择方面的认知负担，从而提供了与高级人工智能功能更简化和直观的交互。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "OpenAI 现在首次在单位成本智能方面占据主导地位。",
    "这是因为单位智能的成本最终是一个路由问题；",
    "如果从 GPT-3 到 GPT-4 的重大突破是混合专家，那么从 GPT-4o/o3 到 GPT-5 的重大突破可能是混合模型（又名“路由器”）。",
    "一旦你有了推理和非推理模式，一旦你有了用于效率或专业化（“专家”）或计算深度的不同推理路径，你基本上在系统中的某个地方有一个路由器...",
    "...各大实验室也没有什么秘密武器，可以用更惨痛的代价来构建混合模型。"
  ],
